org.apache.poi.hpsf

Class Variant

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hpsf.Variant
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    VariantSupport 

    public class Variant
extends java.lang.Object
    The Variant types as defined by Microsoft's COM. In the variant types descriptions the following shortcuts are used:
    • [V] - may appear in a VARIANT
    • [T] - may appear in a TYPEDESC
    • [P] - may appear in an OLE property set
    • [S] - may appear in a Safe Array
    (变体类型由Microsoft COM定义。在变体类型描述中，使用了以下快捷方式：[V] -可能出现在VariANT [T] -可能出现在TYPEDESC [P] -可能出现在PLE属性集[S] -可能出现在安全数组中)

        public static final int VT_FILETIME
        [P] FILETIME. The FILETIME structure holds a date and time associated with a file. This 64-bit value is split into the two dwords stored in the structure.([P]FILETIME。FILETIME结构保存与文件关联的日期和时间。该结构识别一个64位的整数，指定自1601年1月1日以来经过的100微秒间隔的数量。此64位值被拆分为存储在结构中的两个dword。)

      • VT_CLSID

        public static final int VT_CLSID
        [P] A Class ID.

        It consists of a 32 bit unsigned integer indicating the size of the structure, a 32 bit signed integer indicating (Clipboard Format Tag) indicating the type of data that it contains, and then a byte array containing the data.

        The valid Clipboard Format Tags are:

        • Thumbnail.CFTAG_WINDOWS
        • Thumbnail.CFTAG_MACINTOSH
        • Thumbnail.CFTAG_NODATA
        • Thumbnail.CFTAG_FMTID
        
 typedef struct tagCLIPDATA {
 // cbSize is the size of the buffer pointed to
 // by pClipData, plus sizeof(ulClipFmt)
 ULONG              cbSize;
 long               ulClipFmt;
 BYTE*              pClipData;
 } CLIPDATA;
        ([P]一个类ID。它由一个32位无符号整数（指示结构的大小）、一个32位有符号整数（指示其包含的数据类型）和一个包含数据的字节数组组成。有效的缩略图格式标记为：缩略图.CFTAG_WINDOWS缩略图.CFTAG_MACINTOSH缩略图.CFTAG_NODATA缩略图.CFTAG_FMTID typedef struct tagCLIPDATA { // cbSize是指向的缓冲区的大小 //通过pClipData，加上sizeof（ulClipFdt） ULONG cbSize; 长 ulClipFMT; 字节 * pClipData; } CLIPDATA;)
        See Also:
        PROPVARIANT structure, Constant Field Values

    • Method Detail

      • getVariantName

        public static java.lang.String getVariantName(long variantType)
        Returns the variant type name associated with a variant type number.(返回与变体类型号关联的变体类型名称。)
        Parameters:
        variantType - The variant type number(VariantType -变体类型号)
        Returns:
        The variant type name or the string "unknown variant type"(变体类型名称或字符串“未知变体类型”)

      • getVariantLength

        public static int getVariantLength(long variantType)
        Returns a variant type's length.(返回变体类型的长度。)
        Parameters:
        variantType - The variant type number(VariantType -变体类型号)
        Returns:
        The length of the variant type's data in bytes. If the length is variable, i.e. the length of a string, -1 is returned. If HPSF does not know the length, -2 is returned. The latter usually indicates an unsupported variant type.(变体类型数据的长度（以字节为单位）。如果长度可变，即字符串的长度，则返回-1。如果HPSF不知道长度，则返回-2。后者通常指示不支持的变体类型。)
